  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.94,
      "text": "Let's talk about compound returns."
    },
    {
      "start": 3.14,
      "end": 6.78,
      "text": "When you patch code, each fix has local returns."
    },
    {
      "start": 7.28,
      "end": 8.96,
      "text": "You fixed one bug in one place."
    },
    {
      "start": 9.52,
      "end": 11.74,
      "text": "Similar bugs can still occur elsewhere."
    },
    {
      "start": 12.36,
      "end": 14.82,
      "text": "And sometimes your patch introduces new bugs."
    },
    {
      "start": 15.96,
      "end": 17.9,
      "text": "The returns are linear at best."
    },
    {
      "start": 18.62,
      "end": 19.68,
      "text": "Often sub-linear."
    },
    {
      "start": 21.88,
      "end": 25.38,
      "text": "When you add a test in PDD, the returns are different."
    },
    {
      "start": 26.18,
      "end": 27.66,
      "text": "That test you wrote today"
    },
    {
      "start": 27.66,
      "end": 30.0,
      "text": "it constrains tomorrow's generation"
    },
    {
      "start": 30.0,
      "end": 31.92,
      "text": "and next week's and next years"
    },
    {
      "start": 31.92,
      "end": 33.5,
      "text": "it's a permanent wall."
    },
    {
      "start": 34.42,
      "end": 37.18,
      "text": "Every investment in the mold has compound returns."
    },
    {
      "start": 37.88,
      "end": 40.66,
      "text": "Every investment in patching has diminishing returns."
    },
    {
      "start": 42.86,
      "end": 46.16,
      "text": "Your great-grandmother wasn't stupid for darning socks."
    },
    {
      "start": 47.0,
      "end": 48.6,
      "text": "The economics made it rational."
    },
    {
      "start": 49.96,
      "end": 52.32,
      "text": "And you're not stupid for patching code."
    },
    {
      "start": 52.86,
      "end": 55.56,
      "text": "Until now the economics made it rational"
    },
    {
      "start": 55.56,
      "end": 56.98,
      "text": "but the economics changed"
    },
    {
      "start": 56.98,
      "end": 59.08,
      "text": "and when economics changed,"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.34,
      "end": 63.04,
      "text": "behavior that was rational becomes darning socks."
    }
  ]
}